issues.fix:
Move `getComputedStyle` calls inside the `draw()` function so colors are resolved per frame, or listen for a `prefers-color-scheme` media query change to re-run the effect:
```ts
const mq = window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)');
mq.addEventListener('change', reinitEffect);
return () => mq.removeEventListener('change', reinitEffect);
```
Alternatively, add a `data-theme` attribute or CSS class to the effect dependencies.

